{"tid":2237133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"手足留意以色列公司cellebrite! 槍手投案拒解鎖iPhone　以色列資安公司免費幫破解","createTime":"2020-10-10T04:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T05:05:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1f00f8606844e9570a862b5b01019cc576caee","tid":2237133,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"槍擊館長的劉丞浩投案後，他使用的iPhone XS手機一併被查扣，但劉男拒絕解鎖，專案小組將手機送刑事局解鎖未果，適逢以色列資安公司Cellebrite與刑事局3年合約到期，該公司為爭取續約，提出「免費破解手機1次」服務，正好用來破解劉男手機，未料該手機僅使用1周，與案情相關資料有限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20201009/BDFQGEDUNNGVFKXYFFSRUECS5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2F20201009%2FBDFQGEDUNNGVFKXYFFSRUECS5Q%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=6b8738f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2F20201009%2FBDFQGEDUNNGVFKXYFFSRUECS5Q%2F&h=2c2d1592\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20201009/BDFQGEDUNNGVFKXYFFSRUECS5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"e74f19ec68ab07a536d04f1b598a200cfbb0925f","tid":2237133,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"e1729ee0331069f55dc5c6f1d64e6efdf14d5934","tid":2237133,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"fucking kikes"},{"pid":"99dbb72b0ce053e044b4a6b0945f50af1779e47c","tid":2237133,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1729ee0331069f55dc5c6f1d64e6efdf14d5934","tid":2237133,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"fucking kikes"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHNXxiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHNXxiA.jpg&h=57f7526d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7263b714fc3314404dd5fc9596f9d4501897225","tid":